		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just wanted to say, with the help of kuja killer, we were able to swap out $C000-FFFF, and I made it so links flying sword dpcm is loaded from the new bank, while the other dpcms are still able to be loaded from the original bank.

		

